title: Update/Upgrade Packages Installed by Home-Manager
tags: @zettel _method homemanager nix
roam-id: 192ad245-4004-4632-b82d-10719034fc83
type: text/markdown

- non-flake way

  ``` shell
  nix-channel --update
  home-manager swtich
  ```

- if you're using flakes then

  ``` shell
  cd /path/to/your/flake.nix
  nix flake update
  home-manager swtich
  ```
